OL,3,CCalls to protect 'in danger'
OL,4,CGuernsey's Loophole towers from
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FGuernsey residents are concerned that
OL,8,Ffailure to protect the island's
OL,9,FLoophole towers could see them fall
OL,10,Finto disrepair.
OL,12,FThis comes as the Channel Islands
OL,13,FOccupation Society are concerned that
OL,14,Fthe towers are not being kept in good
OL,15,Fcondition.
OL,17,FToday, 12 towers still survive,
OL,18,Fhowever, three of them have been
OL,19,Fdestroyed in the last century.
