OL,3,CCalls to protect 'in danger'
OL,4,CGuernsey's Loophole towers from
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FWhile none have collapsed due to
OL,8,Fdisrepair, there are concerns over at
OL,9,Fleast two of the towers.
OL,11,FBay de la Jaonneuse's tower has
OL,12,Fstarted to lean to the side and
OL,13,FChouet's tower is situated next to a
OL,14,Fnew quarry where there will be
OL,15,Fblasting to extract granite.
OL,17,FStates of Guernsey archaeologist, Phil
OL,18,Fde Jersey, says: "They will last for
OL,19,Flonger but they might actually need a
OL,20,Fbit more tender loving care as time
OL,21,Fgoes on.
