OL,3,CCalls to protect 'in danger'
OL,4,CGuernsey's Loophole towers from
OL,5,Ccollapse
OL,7,FOliver Brock from the Trust says:
OL,8,F"Building structures will only last so
OL,9,Flong. The water ingress on its own
OL,10,Fwill start to damage the interiors of
OL,11,Fthe walls inside the actual building
OL,12,Ffabric itself.
OL,14,F"The woodwork and floor levels are
OL,15,Falso in danger so there is a concern.
OL,17,F"There's all sorts of uses that can be
OL,18,Fmade of old buildings and bringing
OL,19,Fthem back into use is a, is a really
OL,20,Fgood way of making sure that they're
OL,21,Fcared for."
